#

Bread and Butter Pickles

75 min
$5
50 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

CondimentSnackEasyQuick

Description

A sweet and tangy pickle that perfectly complements sandwiches and BBQ.

Ingredients

  • cucumbers: 4 cups, sliced
  • onion: 1 cup, thinly sliced
  • vinegar: 2 cups, white or apple cider
  • sugar: 2 cups
  • salt: 1/4 cup
  • turmeric: 1 teaspoon
  • celery seeds: 1 teaspoon
  • mustard seeds: 1 teaspoon
  • black peppercorns: 1 teaspoon
